  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The increasing emphasis on food security issues from 2014 has seen the introduction of conservation farming with its principle of crop rotation to Masara farmers under the sustainable maize programme to ensure that agro inputs provided to farmers by companies for main crops can also be used for other food crops to increase food access.</narrative>
